Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Description: Qt wrapper for bluez
 libbluedevil is a Qt-style library for accessing the bluez Bluetooth stack.
 .
 It is used by the KDE Bluetooth stack, BlueDevil.
